過經驗分享，巴絲打請指教<br />\n<br />\n希望唔會造成大家不快"},{"pid":"0d082a11928fa120e4679118da26ffa76ec87e05","tid":1357000,"uid":40321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebda1da679e8304f1edac3d18630013cb1b7b433","tid":1357000,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:16:59.000Z","msg":"果D網友黎架咋,你估兄弟咩,點會救你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:18:38.000Z","msg":"岩 認同   組團搵自己友!"},{"pid":"a0b99c1df9c89fc5fec5d9c3ea81bfea579636ea","tid":1357000,"uid":246020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad332c57086905556d22d2149283e74637deba51","tid":1357000,"uid":246020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"08714001e39584938ddd35f7b0fb8d19635fd6fa","tid":1357000,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"21b41d39b29e260b11196cbf926ace9da0406a25","tid":1357000,"uid":48,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:00:39.000Z","msg":"當日比人打個啲大部分都唔係示威者黎 大部分係放工番屋企既市民<br />\n<br />\n邊個會同你擋"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:01:58.000Z","msg":"嗰班人全部都係特登由上環搭去元朗支援的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:17:34.000Z","msg":"最勇武個班應該仲留左係上環，所以你D隊友應該算係和理非"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"不過希望你都唔會因為咁而唔再出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01e0aae7ff7a75d93c2f73e17b8a0be093a4e80a","tid":1357000,"uid":29188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e1581ef21b3e2cadc44aaaad2e0504e9d3f792b2","tid":1357000,"uid":155253,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:12:56.000Z","msg":"ON9 同個黑警一樣,一個衝出去<br />\n打時打,睇隊友係邊呀<br />\n最ON9就豬隊友,落單一個要人救你,隨時害全隊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T16:19:03.000Z","msg":"對唔住，我朋友廢，戰況混亂未能一眼關七，害咗大家"},{"pid":"8e3039c9b8089f2adbdd610f6e3473e2d43d8f60","tid":1357000,"uid":40321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01e0aae7ff7a75d93c2f73e17b8a